No. 572,

Mise.

McWilliams v. United States. Bernard J. Mellman for petitioner. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, and Philip R. Monahan for the United States.

C. A. 8th Cir. Motion to remand and petition for writ of certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and petition.
